This type of graph is a radar graph (or web, or star, or spider..).  It rates the hits based on five characteristics, Danceability, Loudness, Acousticness, Energy, and Valence (the happiness factor).  The key identifies how the hits from the summer of that particular year compare based on those qualities, with pink meaning the hits are different with respect to these 5 categories to blue meaning the hits are similar with respect to these 5 categories.  What would this show you about the hits from 1988-1991 vs 2015-2018?

